h3. Symptom
As long as there're double quotation mark embedded in JIRA title, e.g. "TEST" (instead of TEST), most of GH pages will throw js exceptions with some malfunctional js operations.

h3. Cause
The js exception is thrown on the below scripts:
{code}
document.title = "GreenHopper Configuration - "TEST""; 
{code}

h3. Workaround
Go to JIRA Administration -> General Configuration, and remove double quotation mark from JIRA title.

